headline: Unlocking Q2 Potential of Rollins (ROL): Exploring Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
summary: Looking beyond Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimate forecasts for Rollins (ROL), delve into some of its key metrics to gain a deeper insight into the company's potential performance for the quarter ended June 2025.

headline: Rollins Gears Up to Report Q2 Earnings: Here's What You Should Know
summary: ROL set to report Q2 results, with earnings and revenues expected to rise nearly 7.4% and 9.8% year over year on broad segment growth.
